description.narrative: To improve child health;standards in emergencies, UNICEF supported the development of two technical guidance for health care workers on “MNH and GBV services” and ;“provision of immunization services&39; in the context of COVID-19”. Support was provided to the Ministry of Health for the procurement of all vaccines through UNICEF Supply Division, resulting in cost-savings. To strengthen national nutrition programming, UNICEF supported the development of the Food and Nutrition Strategy and the Health Sector Nutrition Operational Plan. To enhance elimination of mother-to-child transmission service delivery, UNICEF supported the development of the EMTCT operational plan to be implemented in 2021. | Status:Met | As-of Date:11/01/2021
